        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "When a pass calls for cutting or condensing, you often want to keep the original wording — strong lines, lore, ideas you might reuse later. “Backup to cut file” copies the selected text into a per-scene cut file without changing any review decision. Configure where those cut files live below.",
          "target": "当一轮审阅要求剪切或压缩时，您通常希望保留原始措辞——精彩的句子、背景设定、可能稍后重用的想法。“备份到剪切文件”会将选定文本复制到每个场景的剪切文件中，而不更改任何审阅决定。请在下方配置这些剪切文件的存储位置。"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "How cut files work:",
