          "target": "基于Radial Timeline的跟踪"
        },
        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "Radial Timeline gives Editorialist stable scene IDs in the active book, so revision history stays attached to the right scene even when titles change or scenes are reordered.",
          "target": "Radial Timeline为编辑意见工具在活动书籍中提供稳定的场景ID，因此即使标题更改或场景重新排序，修订历史记录也会附加到正确的场景。"
        },
