        {
          "type": "ObjectProperty",
          "name": "text",
          "source": "This vault is currently falling back to note paths. For accurate rename-safe tracking outside Radial Timeline, inject stable note IDs into tracked notes.",
          "target": "此保险库当前正在回退到笔记路径。为了在Radial Timeline之外实现准确的重命名安全跟踪，请将稳定的笔记ID注入到被跟踪的笔记中。"
